    Lets Scrape the wall of shame from the U.S. Department of Health and Human Services Office for Civil Rights (You could just download the data file, but where is the fun in that!)

    Step 1 - Import all of the libraries you’ll need

    1. requests
    2. pandas
    3. numpy
    4. matplotlib.pyplot
    5. Beautiful Soup
    import requests, pandas, numpy, matplotlib.pyplot
from bs4 import BeautifulSoup

    Step 2 - Download the data

    2.a Use the requests library to grab the content of this page

    https://ocrportal.hhs.gov/ocr/breach/breach_report.jsf

    page = requests.get("https://ocrportal.hhs.gov/ocr/breach/breach_report.jsf")
